  "prompt": "How many people audition for Indian idol every year?",
  "response": "The number of people who audition for Indian Idol each year can vary significantly from season to season. While specific numbers are not always publicly disclosed, it is estimated that tens of thousands of aspiring singers audition for the show annually. For example, in some seasons, reports have indicated that upwards of 100,000 people have tried out. The exact number depends on various factors such as the popularity of the show, the ease of the audition process (which may include online auditions), and regional interest. If you want precise figures for a specific season, it would be best to refer to official announcements or press releases from the show's producers.",
